Instruction Breakdowns:

A1 (4 bit) (R1) (R2)
(1 Byte) ADD (R1) (R2):  #Adding 2 Registers
    MV R1, A    #Move R1 to A. This doesn't preserve A, as A will be the result from the operation
    PUSH B      #Push B to save it
    MV R2, B    #Move R2 to B
    ADD A, B    #Add B to A
    MV B, R2    #Move B back to R2
    POP B       #Restore B

A3 
(2 Byte) ADI (R1) (N1):
    PUSH B
    LDB N1
    MV R1, A
    ADD A, B
    POP B   

